s://www.facebook.com/mvmtv.hk/videos/464039040996709/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmvmtv.hk%2Fvideos%2F464039040996709%2F&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=3db62d28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mvmtv.hk/videos/464039040996709/</a>"},{"pid":"189d62800634f4c0a24a89efed3ebf4096e630d2","tid":1257682,"uid":39412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:30:06.000Z","msg":"睇番舊新聞, 件事2018年12月已經基本破晒, 陳同佳都已經拉埋, 台灣早早出聲要求引渡, 其實唔存在有冤無路訴要搵政黨幫手, 有晒閉路電視行李箱都MATCH, 係唔明起初佢點解搵民記. <br />\n個陣好多人可能未十分留意, 比卡超講好多次要跟&quot;香港法律&quot;, 但就係唔覆. 現在睇係件大伏, 送中多數早有預定, 只係撞到呢單野以為可以食住上, 配合凶案可以博人同情過關"},{"pid":"f6c6c4090449e85681677cd7c88b903272273a57","tid":1257682,"uid":191186,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68bbb2bf12e4e06b0e06c72bf22ea5e726e12a9","tid":1257682,"uid":59030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"416da74ff39fb3f1fd72ca934e77730edda75895","tid":1257682,"uid":9193,"like":1199,"dislike":13,"score":1186,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:25:32.000Z","msg":"本身都好同情佢地<br />\n但搵民建聯幫手就已經知道佢哋係on9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:38:48.000Z","msg":"佢老豆係大陸做汽車零件生意<br />\n典型廢老黎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"分分鐘而家有份鬧後生仔搞亂香港"}]}